Program: Discovery
Title: Weathering the Storm - hurricanes
Link: https://www.bbc.co.uk/programmes/p03jrys6
Last Broadcast Date: 14 September 2004
Looking at the impact of hurricanes, focusing on the aftermath of Hurricane Charley in Florida, USA. The programme is the first in a series examining how we deal with extreme weather. The first in the series reports on hurricanes, the strongest natural force of all. Picture: Hurricane approaching Southeast Asia, Credit: Thinkstock Show less